StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: GETADMIN
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.GETADMIN(cAdmin OUT SYS_REFCURSOR)&lt;br/&gt;IS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; OPEN cAdmin FOR &lt;br/&gt; SELECT Admin_table.idPerson, Admin_table.surname, Admin_table.firstName, &lt;br/&gt; Admin_table.title, Admin_table.address, Admin_table.phone, Admin_table.postcode,&lt;br/&gt; Admin_table.campusLocation, &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Admin_table.idBuilding, Admin_table.numberOffice,&lt;br/&gt; Admin_table.staffType, &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; Admin_table.admiTitle, Admin_table.computerSkill,Admin_table.officeSkill&lt;br/&gt; FROM Admin_table;&lt;br/&gt;END getAdmin;
